  TITLE     Purification and properties of a new glutathione-dependent thiol:disulphide oxidoreductase from rat liver.
  JOURNAL   Biochem. J. 207 (1982) 133-8.
  ORGANISM  Rattus norvegicus
PATHWAY     ec00480  Glutathione metabolism
